Package: bayesfoRest
Type: Package
Title: Creates forest plots for Bayesian meta-analyses
Description: bayesfoRest creates forest plots for Bayesian meta-analyses in data that has been prepared using the metafor and brms packages. 
    In addition to forest plots, posterior probability plots are generated for the overall effect and for the heterogeneity parameter.
Version: 0.0.0.9000
